---
title: Carb Smart Tex-Mex Beef Lettuce Wraps with Tomato-Jalapeño Salsa and Chipotle Drizzle
description: Get ready for a wild ride to flavour town! Ground beef is cooked with savoury Tex-Mex paste and nestled in crisp lettuce wraps with DIY tomato-jalapeño salsa, cheddar cheese and smoky chipotle sauce for a lighter take on tacos.
